Lineage 2 Login Server
----------------------

This folder contains the code used for the login server.
Lineage 2 separates the login from the game itself.


Requirements
------------

- GCC
- Make
- GDB (optional for debug)
- OpenSSL library
- Data structures library from https://github.com/Ruk33/data_structures


Installation
------------

Simply run make on the root folder. A loginserver executable will be generated.
When executed, the login server will listen for connections on port 2106.
